{
  "title": "Home IDS 🛡️ Tier 1: Master Triage Hub (Ultimate SOC Edition)",
  "uid": "ids-master-hub-ultimate",
  "tags": ["ids", "hub", "soc", "showcase", "production"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "PROMETHEUS_DS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "label": "Prometheus Source"
      },
      {
        "name": "LOKI_DS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "loki",
        "label": "Loki Source"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Navigation Matrix",
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### **🧭 Triage Hub** | [📊 DNS & ML Diagnostics](/d/ids-tier2-dns/home-ids-tier-2-dns-ml-diagnostics?var-device=.*) | [🔒 Network & Lateral (Zeek NDR)](/d/ids-tier2-ndr/home-ids-tier-2-network-lateral-zeek-ndr?var-device=.*) | [🌍 GeoIP & OSINT Intel](/d/ids-tier2-geo/home-ids-tier-2-geoip-osint-intel?var-device=.*) | [⚙️ Engine System Health](/d/ids-system-health/home-ids-tier-2-engine-system-health?var-device=.*)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Infrastructure & IPS Health",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### ⚙️ Engine Health & Mitigation Status\n* **Pipeline Lag & EPS:** Verifies the Python engine is processing Zeek and Pi-hole databases in real-time. If lag exceeds 5s, the engine is bottlenecked.\n* **IPS Armed & Actions:** Shows if the script is allowed to modify the network. *Pi-hole Blocks* indicate domains injected into gravity. *Network Drops* indicate MAC addresses severed at the router via webhook."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Zeek NDR Status",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_status", "legendFormat": "Status" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "mappings": [ { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "ONLINE", "color": "green" }, "0": { "text": "OFFLINE", "color": "red" } } } ] } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "IPS Mitigation Armed",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_ips_enabled", "legendFormat": "Status" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "mappings": [ { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "ARMED", "color": "blue" }, "0": { "text": "DISABLED", "color": "orange" } } } ] } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "IPS Pi-hole Blocks (1h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "sum(increase(home_ids_ips_pihole_blocks_total[1h])) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Blocked Domains" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "orange" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "IPS Network Drops (1h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "sum(increase(home_ids_ips_router_isolations_total[1h])) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Severed MACs" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pipeline Lag (DB Sync)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_collector_lag_seconds", "legendFormat": "Lag" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 5, "color": "yellow" }, { "value": 15, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pipeline Alerts Fired (1h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "increase(home_ids_alerts_total[1h])", "legendFormat": "Alerts" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "orange" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Macro Threat Overview",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🌍 Macro Threat Overview\n* **Live Baseline Breaches:** Devices violating their own mathematical limits right now.\n* **Anti-Poison Freezes:** Devices that are exhibiting threat behavior and have been locked out of teaching the Machine Learning engine (prevents malware from making its own traffic look 'normal').\n* **Severe Threats:** Active devices requiring human intervention (Risk Score ≥ 6.0)."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active Devices Monitored",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_risk_score) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Devices" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "blue" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Engine Max Risk Score",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 4, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "max(home_ids_risk_score) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Max Risk" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 4, "color": "orange" }, { "value": 6, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Severe Threats (Risk ≥ 6.0)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 9, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_risk_score >= 6.0) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Threats" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Live Baseline Breaches",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 14, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_query_rate > home_ids_query_rate_threshold_limit) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Breaches" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "orange" }, { "value": 3, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Anti-Poison Freezes",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 19, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_baseline_poisoned == 1) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Frozen Nodes" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: The 3-Step Threat Hunt",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🚨 The 3-Step Threat Hunt (Master Ledger)\n**Step 1. Check the Risk Score & IPS Blocks:** Any device at the top of the table (Red Risk) is anomalous. If 'IPS Blocks' is > 0, the script is actively fighting the device by blacklisting domains. \n**Step 2. Identify the Threat Vector:**\n* **High ML Score & High Blocked Ratio?** The device is acting strange and failing lookups. Click its Hostname and open **DNS & ML Diagnostics** to check for DGA Ransomware.\n* **TI Match Flag = 1?** The device queried a known hacker domain. Click its Hostname and open **GeoIP & OSINT** to see the AbuseIPDB/VirusTotal sandbox details.\n* **Zeek Notices or JA3 Hash > 0?** Network-level threat. Click its Hostname and open **Zeek NDR** to check for Data Exfiltration or Lateral Network Scans.\n**Step 3. Verify Probation:** If Probation = 1, the device is brand new to the network. The AI is highly sensitive to it, so false positives are possible until it establishes a 24-hour baseline."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "🚨 Master Threat Ledger (Click Hostname to Investigate)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 16, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "home_ids_risk_score", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "A" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_ml_anomaly_score", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "B" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_ti_risk", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "C" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_ti_match", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "D" },
        { "expr": "sum by (hostname) (increase(home_ids_ips_pihole_blocks_total[1h]))", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "E" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_query_rate_threshold_limit", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "F" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_blocked_ratio", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "G" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_conn_count", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "H" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_lateral_moves", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "I" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_notices", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "J" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_ja3_malicious", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "K" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_probation_status", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "L" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_safe_device", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "M" }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "joinByField", "options": { "byField": "hostname", "mode": "outer" } },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "Time 1": true, "Time 2": true, "Time 3": true, "Time 4": true, "Time 5": true, "Time 6": true, "Time 7": true, "Time 8": true, "Time 9": true, "Time 10": true, "Time 11": true, "Time 12": true, "Time 13": true, "__name__": true, "device": true, "device_type": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "hostname": "Hostname",
              "Value #A": "Live Risk",
              "Value #B": "ML Score",
              "Value #C": "TI Threat",
              "Value #D": "TI Match Flag",
              "Value #E": "IPS Blocks Fired",
              "Value #F": "Baseline Limit",
              "Value #G": "Blocked Ratio",
              "Value #H": "Zeek Conns",
              "Value #I": "Zeek Lateral Moves",
              "Value #J": "Zeek Notices",
              "Value #K": "JA3 Hash",
              "Value #L": "Probation",
              "Value #M": "Safe Listed"
            }
          }
        },
        { "id": "sortBy", "options": { "fields": [ { "desc": true, "displayName": "Live Risk" } ] } }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "center" } },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Hostname" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  { "title": "📈 Open Forensic Room: AI Behavioral & DGA Diagnostics", "url": "/d/ids-tier2-dns/home-ids-tier-2-dns-ml-diagnostics?var-device=${__data.fields.Hostname}", "targetBlank": true },
                  { "title": "🔒 Open Forensic Room: Zeek NDR & Network Exfiltration", "url": "/d/ids-tier2-ndr/home-ids-tier-2-network-lateral-zeek-ndr?var-device=${__data.fields.Hostname}", "targetBlank": true },
                  { "title": "🌍 Open Forensic Room: GeoIP Matrix & OSINT Mapping", "url": "/d/ids-tier2-geo/home-ids-tier-2-geoip-osint-intel?var-device=${__data.fields.Hostname}", "targetBlank": true },
                  { "title": "🪵 Open Forensic Room: Streamed Loki Logs Audit", "url": "/explore?orgId=1&left=%5B%22now-3h%22,%22now%22,%22${LOKI_DS}%22,%7B%22expr%22:%22%7Bjob%3D\\\"home_ids_alerts\\\"%7D%20%7C%20json%20%7C%20device_hostname%3D\\\"${__data.fields.Hostname}\\\"%22%7D%5D", "targetBlank": true }
                ]
              },
              { "id": "custom.align", "value": "left" }
            ]
          },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Live Risk" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 4 }, { "color": "red", "value": 6 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ML Score" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "IPS Blocks Fired" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "TI Match Flag" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "JA3 Hash" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Zeek Lateral Moves" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Probation" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Safe Listed" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "transparent", "value": 0 }, { "color": "blue", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Blocked Ratio" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.8 } ] } } ] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: IPS Mitigation Audit",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 43 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🛡️ Automated IPS Audit Ledger\nUse this section to review exactly what the script has done to your network. \n* **Domains Automatically Blocked:** Shows exactly which domain was blocked via Pi-hole and what device caused it. *If a legitimate app breaks, copy the domain from this list and add it to `safe_domains` in your `config.json`.*\n* **IPS Errors / Failures:** Shows if the script attempted to block a threat but was rejected by the router or Pi-hole API.\n* **Safe-Listed Devices:** Shows devices explicitly exempted from IPS quarantine in your configuration."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "🛑 Domains Automatically Blocked by Script (Pi-hole IPS)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 47 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (hostname, domain) (increase(home_ids_ips_pihole_blocks_total[$__range])) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "hostname": "Target Device",
              "domain": "Blocked Domain",
              "Value": "Times Blocked"
            }
          }
        },
        { "id": "sortBy", "options": { "fields": [ { "desc": true, "displayName": "Times Blocked" } ] } }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "left" } },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Times Blocked" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } },
              { "id": "custom.displayMode", "value": "color-background" },
              { "id": "custom.align", "value": "center" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "⚠️ IPS Errors (Failed Mitigations)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 47 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (target_type) (increase(home_ids_ips_errors_total[$__range])) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "target_type": "Failing API Route",
              "Value": "Error Count"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "center" } },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Error Count" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } },
              { "id": "custom.displayMode", "value": "color-text" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "🛡️ Active Safe-Listed Devices (Exempt from Quarantine)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 52 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "home_ids_safe_device > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "device": true, "device_type": true, "__name__": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "hostname": "Whitelisted Device",
              "Value": "Status"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "center" } },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Status" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "valueMappings",
                "value": [
                  { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "color": "blue", "index": 0, "text": "SAFE LISTED" } } }
                ]
              },
              { "id": "custom.displayMode", "value": "color-background" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}